The sunlight dances across the raptors' feathers, turning them into a blur of brilliant colors. The brachiosaurs bask in the warm glow, their skin shimmering with an otherworldly radiance. The scene is framed by the distant mountains, their peaks swathed in a purple haze. The lake is the focal point, a tranquil oasis in the midst of an ancient world, inviting you to step back in time and experience the majesty of prehistory. --ar 3:2** - <@1062034531504369784> (relaxed)
